You can use this grid system to create a layout based on multiple column grid system, either a regular grid system or a pushed with a sidebar on the left side. This packages also contains the tokens that is presented under information tab and also the spacing tokens available under [spacing](/foundation/spacing). 

**SASS**

In the grid system package we created ready mixins,maps and tokens to be imported in your application for your beneifit.

```
// First, import mixin and tokens file in your SASS environment
@import '~node_modules/@scania/grid/dist/scss/grid';
```

If you want to know how place different elements and component inside the grid system, then you can use layout and element tokens to define that. you can read more about them in [spacing](/foundation/spacing) section

```
//Layout token
padding: $spacing-layout-12;

//Element tokens
$spacing-element-2: 0.5rem; // 2px

```

